[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 4, chOption: W, chBasis: S, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:3, nBasis: 2, nRot: 1, useStandardVul: true"]
[VersionToken "1de3bd2006e47ebedf09973e7b3732d9a4cbf847760473386accb327543a1829"]
[Category "Partnership Bidding"]
[Difficulty "advanced"]
[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/roman_key_card"]
[Student "S"]
{EAST needs to know how many Aces WEST holds.

One way to find out would be to bid 3\S, (which is forcing), then launch Blackwood.

Another way is to bid 4\C (Gerber) right now.

The first way is probably better but we needed a Gerber example.}

